include/helpers/hyksort_helper.h and include/omp/omp_utils.h is refactored below algorithm 'HykSort'

Hari Sundar, Dhairya Malhotra and George Biros.HykSort: A New Variant of Hypercube Quicksort on Distributed Memory Architectures
http://www.cs.utah.edu/~hari/files/pubs/ics13.pdf

